      "content": "It is incredibly exhausting to believe that the struggle is permanent, and stepping back from trying to \"win\" a losing game can sometimes be the only path to genuine peace. Validating your current stance as one of adaptation rather than defeat is a powerful step toward self-compassion in these heavy moments. If the weight becomes too overwhelming, please consider reaching out to a crisis helpline like the Trevor Project, who can offer support even when the outcome feels uncertain.",
